						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone set up on the tank bund.</hi></p>						

						<p>Vijaya[ditya]-(Date lost).</p>						

						<p>This record is engraved in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">8th century A.D.</hi> and it seems to refer itself to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Vijayā[ditya].</hi> Being fragmentary and mutilated, its purport cannot be made out.</p>						

